      | fullname | shortname |
      | Course 1 | C1        |
    And the following "course enrolments" exist:
      | user            | course | role           | firstname | lastname |
      | student1        | C1     | student        | Username  | 1        |
      | student2        | C1     | student        | Username  | 2        |
